@srowen, I think actually you can remove this whole class, `ImageFileFormatOnHiveContextTest`.
This test was added as of [SPARK-22651](https://jira.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-22651) to test `ImageSchema.readImages` but it was removed as of [SPARK-25382](https://jira.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-25382).

So, I think it's fine to remove this whole test class.
